    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: All </p><p></p><p>You specialize in higher quality materials to improve the durability of your Puppet Tools.</p><p> This Upgrade changes depending on your chosen technique; </p><p>• Black/Blue/Green: Increase the hit points of your Puppet Tool by +10.<br /> For each level after 2nd level, increase your Puppet's hit points by +2.<br /> You can take this upgrade multiple times, once for each puppet tool you have.</p><p> • Purple: Your armor gains a +1 bonus to its AC calculation, and gains +3 DR against bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage.</p><p> • Red: Increase the hit points of all of your Puppet Tools by +5.<br /> For each level after 2nd level, increase their hit points by +1.</p><p> • White: Increase your hit points by +1 for each level you have in this class.<br /> If your Weaver Gloves are ever removed, you lose this increase to your maximum hit points, though this cannot cause you to go below 1 hp.</p><p></p>",
